  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    LightLocalizer
    This class is used to localize the robot using the Light Sensors
    Main
    The main driver class for the lab.
    Navigation
    This class is used to navigate the robot around the playing field
    Odometer
    The odometer class keeps track of the robot's (x, y, theta) position.
    Resources
    Helper class that contains all static final variables and wifi components
    Resources.Point
    Represents a coordinate point on the competition map grid.
    Resources.Region
    Represents a region on the competition map grid, delimited by its lower-left and upper-right corners (inclusive).
    UltrasonicLocalizer
    This class is used to localize the robot using the Ultrasonic Sensor
